metadata.name: Pixel OctoPeeps Kingdoms #1
metadata.description: Pixel OctoPeeps Kingdoms is a collection of 4,848 pixel & half-body OctoPeeps NFTs stored on Ethereum Blockchain. Generated programmatically from source images of OctoPeeps Kingdoms collection. Owning a OctoPeeps Kingdoms NFT means you can mint a pixel analogue. Each OctoPeeps Kingdoms NFT only allows one pixel mint, once a Pixel OctoPeeps is minted the original OctoPeeps cannot be used again to mint. More info on https://octopeeps.com
